title: Maggie Beer's Big Mission
overview: In Maggie Beer's Big Mission, Australia's food icon, Maggie Beer, leads an ambitious world first social experiment to transform the meals and dining experience at an aged care home.These resources have been designed by one of the show's experts, Change Care Consultant and Occupational Therapist Elizabeth Oliver, to give you a better understanding of the positive steps taken during the series to work towards improvements for residents and staff.
